    }

As Bohemian points out the list of constants can be static so it&#39;s accessible in more than one place.

For anyone interested, the list in my example is using [double brace initialization][1]. Since I ran into it recently I&#39;ve found it nice for writing quick &amp; dirty list initializations.


  [1]: http://kzeil.home.xs4all.nl/en/project/java/initializer-block.html

Do you want to switch to this??

    switch(x) {
        case 12:
        case 16:
        case 19: 
            //Do something
            break;
